{"tid":1572133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好撚大鑊，今晚之後要大大力推文宣","createTime":"2019-09-15T15:07:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T02:32:22.000Z","uid":124144,"like":42,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"ee68dff8918afcf991ea10bddea7659a17f12748","tid":1572133,"uid":124144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:07:35.000Z","msg":"對家今晚無啦啦唔係點拉人，格硬逼啲手足去北角方向，如果佢要拉人嘅佢一早強力鎮壓啦！<br />\n<br />\n逼咗啲人去北角之後，佢事先安排一堆福建幫喺北角撩交打(福建幫唔會無啦啦出現，一定係有人喺後面煽動)，再特登俾啲廢中，廢老各位手足打到佢仆街。<br />\n<br />\n之後凌晨就會出嚟話示威者好暴力呀，打傷平民呀等等。<br />\n<br />\n各位手足可能會話屌721,831呢，但係你要明白佢做呢啲嘢係做俾淺黃，深藍睇嘅。政府之後就會同國際社會話示威者好暴力架，失晒控，從而嘗試阻止國際戰線<br />\n<br />\n唔係話唔俾手足私了廢老，但係唔好搞出人命，打完廢老之後記得推返啲文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40321c2729bac513522d9ecbf40ea7c27fbf7715","tid":1572133,"uid":124144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:07:58.000Z","msg":"1001"},{"pid":"2bf540664535c63d566a17dc3523a2ee76786349","tid":1572133,"uid":124144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:08:11.000Z","msg":"1002"},{"pid":"dda06095749b1ac783d3dca76395fda1663abf72","tid":1572133,"uid":124144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:08:21.000Z","msg":"1003"},{"pid":"03b111eac63ceec585fe7ede4516b075d8e18482","tid":1572133,"uid":258370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:08:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0d6737304c55d3cee73473b94b80e23b59cf758a","tid":1572133,"uid":124144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:08:32.000Z","msg":"1004"},{"pid":"79fd2dd134549dcac656c14b7a8b411a45c8f72a","tid":1572133,"uid":124144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:08:44.000Z","msg":"1005"},{"pid":"883ac1494029cf70a4f894de04faa58b489fe3c9","tid":1572133,"uid":124144,"like":0,"d